&lt;/ul></description></item><item><title>2024-12-01 코칭 훈련</title><link>https://aquacrew.co.kr/p/2024-12-01-%EC%BD%94%EC%B9%AD-%ED%9B%88%EB%A0%A8/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://aquacrew.co.kr/p/2024-12-01-%EC%BD%94%EC%B9%AD-%ED%9B%88%EB%A0%A8/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://aquacrew.co.kr/p/2024-12-01-%EC%BD%94%EC%B9%AD-%ED%9B%88%EB%A0%A8/2024-12-01-11-20-16.jpeg" alt="Featured image of post 2024-12-01 코칭 훈련" />&lt;ul>
